rows.label: qst720503_msg0002
rows.name: They were tougher than I expected.

rows.label: qst720503_msg0003
rows.name:
I told you so.
You underestimate your opponents.

rows.label: qst720503_msg0004
rows.name:
But at least they can start
repairing the bridge now.

rows.label: qst720503_msg0006
rows.name:
Laura, when we get back to camp,
would you mind training with me again?

rows.label: qst720503_msg0007
rows.name:
Sure, but...
didn't we just finish fighting?

rows.label: qst720503_msg0009
rows.name:
If we don't retrain Hikari a bit,
I'm worried about what's to come.

rows.label: qst720503_msg0010
rows.name: What?! Why does it have to be about me?!

rows.label: qst720503_msg0011
rows.name:
You've been slacking off a bit lately.
If you don't shape up, you won't be
ready when we get a lead on Metsu.

rows.label: qst720503_msg0012
rows.name:
"Slacking," "shape up"... you're talking
about my attitude, right?

rows.label: qst720503_msg0013
rows.name: What else would I be talking about?

rows.label: qst720503_msg0015
rows.name:
Fine! Train me or whatever!
I'll get into shape!

rows.label: qst720503_msg0017
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]What on earth is she angry about...?
